FORMAN--Jo-Nan (nee Lemeshnik), 65, passed away peacefully on Tuesday, January 1, 2008 in Boca Raton, FL. Formally of White Plains, NY, daugther of the late William and Shirley Lemeshnik. She is survived by her husband, Jerome G. Forman; sons, Lloyd, Scott (Susan), and Glenn; grandsons, Andrew and Joshua; and a great many close relatives and friends. Memorial contributions may be made to the American Cancer Society, Hospice By The Sea of Boca Raton or the charity of donor's choice. Services will be private.
